{"tid":564660,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC 做唔掂？ 總裁張嘉臨辭職！","createTime":"2018-02-18T08:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T04:43:47.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd731ce46dc87073f8b5bec2346cfa0f52a6eb4","tid":564660,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"HTC 總裁張嘉臨於昨日以個人職業生涯規劃為理由，正式辭去 HTC 總裁一職。自去年9月 HTC 售 Pixel 手機代工團隊給 Google 後，HTC 再次失去多一個總要的負責人，而 HTC方面，暫時未公佈繼任人選，這個空缺預計暫時由王雪紅接管。<br />\n<br />\n張嘉臨自2012年加入 HTC，HTC 發聲名感謝張在過去六年對公司的貢獻，並祝願他在未來的工作中取得成功。HTC 於去年12月發佈了13年來最差的一份月度財報，HTC 雖然在2017 年度推出了多款受關注的機款，不過都未能改變銷售疲弱的局面，HTC 手機能否在未來一兩年能否仍然存在在市場上？就要睇睇邊個來接手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/02/htc-%E5%81%9A%E5%94%94%E6%8E%82%EF%BC%9F-%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%BC%B5%E5%98%89%E8%87%A8%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%EF%BC%81.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2018%2F02%2Fhtc-%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%258E%2582%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%2587%25A8%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%25EF%25BC%2581.html&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6e14ed14\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/02/htc-%E5%81%9A%E5%94%94%E6%8E%82%EF%BC%9F-%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%BC%B5%E5%98%89%E8%87%A8%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%EF%BC%81.html</a>"},{"pid":"e59d41d6d17e5922375ba1933e7a80c0450cea36","tid":564660,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"在宏達電(hTC)內權力僅次董事長王雪紅的第2把交椅張嘉臨，在雞年尾閃辭引發業界震撼。張嘉臨受訪時直言，智慧手機產業走向商品化，附加價值愈來愈低，連規模很大的南韓三星，在中國大陸市佔率都只剩下1%，他1年前就已提出請辭，只是雙方在尋求一個「比較好」的宣布時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180216000064-260410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180216000064-260410&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3e21cfc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180216000064-260410</a>"},{"pid":"7925f83b31181402ab24c9a428d08130cf3ff46a","tid":564660,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">hTC高層強震 張嘉臨自起爐灶</span></strong></span><br />\n「與王雪紅討論1年」 手機事業總經理將自設AI公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/finance/daily/20180215/37934264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2F20180215%2F37934264&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d73c7e9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2F20180215%2F37934264&h=75a8397f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/finance/daily/20180215/37934264</a><br />\n<br />\n他昨接受採訪時表示，與董事長王雪紅討論長達1年，待Google收購宏達電手機代工部門交易完成後，要一圓從大學研究所時期就有的創業夢，新AI公司已有初步的雛形和規劃，預計3月細節會出來，台灣也會成立分公司。"},{"pid":"5066fa37b1684fcde0bc3b08d8d07e5606fe3464","tid":564660,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"就執"},{"pid":"f55164fb47ab75513fe38e3d2be538db2438d69a","tid":564660,"uid":41658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5066fa37b1684fcde0bc3b08d8d07e5606fe3464","tid":564660,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"就執"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"手機界atv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463777bb64fb15637c71ab6ccdb57b2d11c7fb9d","tid":564660,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"年年話執年年都未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張嘉臨任內幾年都唔係做得好"},{"pid":"d5911a150a24ddea6e6b05f7b142afa7f6423a8e","tid":564660,"uid":33868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"Help this 